The paper discusses the use of content-based data retrieval technology combined with visual analytics to improve data perception and analytical possibilities. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.DB (databases), cs.IR (information retrieval), cs.HC (human-computer interaction), cs.AI (artificial intelligence), and cs.DL (machine learning).
